snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Cleanup Crew - Employee Assessment Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome employee to Hextor Robotics. Before you can begin working with us, for the safety of our brand and our partnership with Fazbear Entertainment, Ltd., we ask you take an employee assessment to see if you'll be a good fit for the role.

PLAYABLE TEASER AVAILABLE MAY 16TH on GAMEJOLT!
https://gamejolt.com/games/fnafcleanupcrew/652841

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY'S: CLEANUP CREW
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hide from animatronics and sneak your way through environments on the exciting Story Mode, discovering the deepest and darkest secrets that lurk within a mysterious partner to Fazbear Entertainment.

Alternatively, you can challenge your skills and try to survive the night while staying hidden from the animatronic threats on Survival Mode.

Or even test your skills and creativity by playing Custom Night, where players online can create their own Five Nights at Freddy's inspired environments and challenge their friends.

More information about this free-roam first-person stealth horror game will be revealed over time. Featuring a full original story mode and various bonus modes and features as well.

This game is being developed live on Twitch. Follow the development here:
https://www.twitch.tv/Kanomics

Thank you for all your ever going support.
All the respect for Scott Cawthon's original work.

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/Kanomics
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/Kanomics
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@Kanomics
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Kanomics
